// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL8-9_Task_01 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - OpenTheSafe 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3889936682" "<color orange>You open the case to find the artifact you're looking for. It's shaped like a large, disfigured eye. As you reach out to grab it, you hear something move around you.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P3064045601" "(Look around)"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1385188953" "<color orange>You see steam-powered cameras appear, along with a large television screen. All the cameras focus on you, while the screen shows the image of you on multiple television screens throughout Paragon City!<br><br>It appears the Nemesis army was planning on putting their ritual on for everyone to see. People begin to gather at the television screens, pointing to you.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P3771702165" "... Er."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1088881842" "<color orange>The people of Paragon wait in anticipation, wondering what you're going to do with this artifact. You notice there's also a few members of the Paragon Police Department watching as well. You <i>may</i> want to consider putting on an act that you're going to move forward to further stop this Nemesis plot. It'll get you some respect from the people and keep the PPD off of your back.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1971261435" "(Explain to the cameras that you're here to save the day)"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1435100249" "<color orange>As you finish, you hear someone running forward to attack you!</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2934353411" "(Say something heroic before leaping into action!)"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DocQuantum 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3767871177" "Hold on a second, {HeroName}. We can work this out. A deal! I'll pay you good money for that artifact, {HeroName}."
// Answer Text :
"P934747977" "I get the feeling you won't have enough, Mangle."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1268095388" "So you have scruples about who you're going to sell it to?! You know, whoever is going to have that artifact just needs to have the proper ritual to summon in the soldiers of Rularuu! Just give it here and I'll finish it!"
// Answer Text :
"P465178097" "Sorry, but this artifact isn't for sale. Especially not for you."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P4014985930" "Give it here, or <i>else</i> {HeroName}!"
// Answer Text :
"P2444566775" "(Knock out Mangle)"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P643115228" "<color orange>You swiftly knock out Mangle!</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1269292275" "Job well done, me."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1109299853" "Having the forces of Rularuu wander the streets of Paragon would definitely cause an issue with various deals you could have here. If you can get this artifact that the Nemesis army has into your hands, you could sell it for a huge amount of money within the Isles. You'll just have to stop the Nemesis army and Mangle from finishing this ritual in order to make yourself some money!"
// AcceptString :
"P1453551616" "Stop the ritual and steal the artifact!"
// SendOffString :
"P3593993123" "You look at the steam powered pidgeon and take down the warehouse where this ritual is taking place. Rularuu must not be impressed that his dominion over Earth is trying to be restarted within a warehouse by a bunch of soldiers using steam-powered guns."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2512838337" "Steal the Shadow Shard Artifact"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3174969170" "You'll need to act fast before the ritual is complete!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1143176022" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Steam Powered Pigeon</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2132036691" "The entire warehouse reeks of steam. You'll have to move in quick to find that artifact."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3652326024" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Steam Powered Pigeon</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You're greeted outside by the applause of several civilians, along with Gregor Richardson of MAGI, who says he is here to take the artifact back to the MAGI vault. With all the eyes of the civilians and some officers on you, you hand over the artifact with a forced smile.<br><br>It's the MAGI vault anyway, you're sure that it'll be back on the market in no time."

