// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL8-9_Task_02 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Hostage 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3519508382" "Jennifer's Dilemma"
// DetailString :
"P2778790149" "You were going to hold this woman for ransom, but it looks like Malta has rigged her to explode! If something isn't done soon, this poor woman is going to be blown up, along with this entire warehouse. It looks like you're the only one who can save her life!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P4126564341" "There are always opportunities to make some cash within Paragon City. Malta thinks they're going to be able to hold this woman for hostage and get away with it, but they're not expecting someone like you to show up to 'save the day', for the right price, of course."
// AcceptString :
"P2531656356" "Take Malta's ransom money for yourself!"
// SendOffString :
"P2903793420" "You've got the address of the warehouse they're in. You'll have to be sure to be careful; knowing Malta, there's a real possibility this is a trap."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P4259255411" "Steal Malta's Ransom Money"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2762044840" "You'll have to move quickly before the PPD arrive!"
// TaskTitle :
"P748441193" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Bootleg Video Case</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3617650617" "From the looks of things, you've managed to arrive before the PPD. Time to make your move to get some money!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3794961854" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Bootleg Video Case</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You walk out of the warehouse to see Jennifer Colin outside with a PPD escort. The officers glare at you, but Jennifer explains that you are the only reason she's alive right now. The officers nod in respect to you while Jennifer gives you her undying gratitude.<br><br>You may have lost your chance for a large payday, but at least you've gained yourself some reputation with the authorities in Paragon. Hopefully that's a good thing."

