// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1202474238" "Talk about being between a rock and a hard place. You may have to expend some precious resources to handle this situation, but the alternative is something you don't want to see. If Hollow Point gets away with this plan, it could cause some serious trouble for the entire <i>world</i>, not to mention just the very fact of Hollow Point's ego being boosted if he succeeds.<br><br>If it's up to you to make a move and save the day, you'll have to bite the bullet and do so."
// AcceptString :
"P2778090734" "Stop Hollow Point and Polar Shift"
// SendOffString :
"P666776185" "You're able to find the location that was given to you over the radio. You'll have to ensure that Hollow Point and Polar Shift are stopped and the technology they're using to amplify Polar Shift's powers is also destroyed."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2718762753" "Stop Paragon from Freezing Over"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1816137855" "If you don't move fast, you may just be turned into an ice sculpture!"
// TaskTitle :
"P3190261099" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hello? Bonjour? Ciao? HOLA?!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2005138460" "You enter the facility which will be the center point for all of Paragon freezing over if you don't stop Hollow Point's plans."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1996076286" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hello? Bonjour? Ciao? HOLA?!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You step outside of the tech lab to see that it's business as usual within Paragon City. None of the citizens know just how close they came to becoming frozen statues. No one may know what you did today, but at least you can carry on with your business in Paragon, for now."

