"P3631921081" "You saved all the heroes and discovered the identity of the mysterious blogger: Flambeaux!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P2396827168" "I heard that Flambeaux has been going around impersonating people on the blogosphere!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL8-9_Task_05 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - LegacyDialog 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P647402583" "Help! It's horrible! They're going to make me into a slave, I don't want to be a slave! I just want to go back to the way things were!"
// Answer Text :
"P1048776185" "I'm guessing you're Mary?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P462099590" "I-I am! You have to help me get out of here!"
// Answer Text :
"P3954091855" "... You're pretty close to 'out' already."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P890782403" "I... I know. I just can't leave knowing that Jason is in there! I managed to get away from them, but even now they're looking for me, hoping to brainwash me with one of their masks!<br><br>Please, you have to destroy the mask they have for me and save Jason!"
// Answer Text :
"P2369876158" "Just make sure you get out of here, alright?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P14904133" "Okay, I will. Thank you so much!"
// Answer Text :
"P2385719541" "(Leave)"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Soul 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P8653302" "Jason's Lost Soul"
// DetailString :
"P2907627065" "You rescued Jason, only to discover that the Carnival have extracted his soul! You'll need to locate and free his soul in order to get him back in one piece."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1948831505" "There's no money involved in this job, but the Carnival of Shadows are clearly showing how unprofessional they are regarding the whole hostage deal. You never kill off the hostages that quickly, that's just how you cross that line from interested in money to interested in destruction.<br><br>Someone's got to save those kids and show the Carnie how a <i>true</i> professional handles things."
// AcceptString :
"P935998136" "Rescue the kidnapped gamers!"
// SendOffString :
"P258413900" "You're able to figure out the location of the building where the Carnies should be. You'll just need to find Jason and Mary and get them out of there, all while showing the Carnies that this is <i>not</i> the way you do business."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1702126131" "Rescue the Kidnapped Gamers"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P473993012" "If you don't act fast, those two gamers will be turned into mindless zombies!"
// TaskTitle :
"P395328397" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Pair of Broken Six Sided Dice</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1268418096" "You see a woman sobbing uncontrollably as you enter. Is that Mary?"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P855408319" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Pair of Broken Six Sided Dice</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You leave the warehouse to be greeted by Jason and Mary, both of whom are holding two pieces of paper, asking for your autograph. They tell you that they're going to tell all their friends about what you did today and how you saved them. {Hero.gender=male Jason|Mary} takes a picture of your outfit and says that they're going to go cosplay as you at the next Super Con."

