// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL8-9_Task_06 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - MissThystle 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2831558929" "<color orange>You find the Rikti crate, which will hopefully contain the weapon supplies that you're looking for.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1512851349" "(Crack open the crate)"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3033886272" "<color orange>You open the crate and see that there are no weapons, but instead small canisters of biological chemicals. Examining them, you get the sense that these chemicals are meant to do something <i>very</i> unfortunate to humans. Some of the images around the crate seem to suggest that they are used to infect humans to turn them into monstrous freaks, like the Lost!</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P3583218724" "(Look around for anything else of note)"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1152012002" "<color orange>You can't seem to find anything else that's just a simple plasma cannon or what not within the crate. All that's in there are chemical vials meant to transform normal human beings into sick, twisted creatures.<br><br>Selling this on the market is only going to come back to cause you problems, mainly when you're swarmed by whatever this chemical mutates! It's best if you destroy these now and ensure the city is safe enough for you to make some money in the future.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2367324493" "(Destroy the chemical crate)"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P232821230" "<color orange>You destroy the crate, and in the process hear someone yelling for help in the distance. Well... you <i>are</i> already here, and maybe it might be someone who has some money."
// Answer Text :
"P953267960" "(Look into the situation)"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - AdministerSerum 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2399762365" "Polar Shift's Willing Compliance"
// DetailString :
"P2030780721" "YOU HAVE ADMINISTERED THE SERUM THAT YOU WERE GIVEN BY MISS THYSTLE.  POLAR SHIFT IS NOW UNDER HER CONTROL AND OFF TO WHEREVER IT IS THAT SHE'S SUPPOSED TO GO.  NOW TO GET YOUR MONEY."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P887588762" "It's not necessarily <i>criminal</i> behavior to steal from the Rikti and sell their weapons off. Whoever is going to use them definitely won't be doing it to do something like <i>invade this dimension</i>. Unless it's being sold to Emperor Cole and his army. You'll just have to make sure that you're a little picky about who you're selling to."
// AcceptString :
"P3343180573" "Raid the Rikti and steal their supplies!"
// SendOffString :
"P1906718644" "The hidden Rikti base appears to be nearby. You'll be doing Paragon a little favor by taking out this Rikti base, and you'll earn yourself some money on the side."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2726866374" "Raid the Rikti Base!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P364801080" "Don't take too long, or you might find someone else taking advantage of this situation!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1082389807" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Replica Rikti Sword</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2450873648" "You see signs of a furious battle along the walls. Something isn't right around here. You'll have to look around to see what's happening with those supplies."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3990447745" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Replica Rikti Sword</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The two heroes you helped are long gone by now. Just goes to show how much thanks someone like you gets in this city.<br><br>At least you were able to stop the Rikti from turning regular people into monsters. You can rest easy knowing that people with a lot of money to spare are going to still be human; at least long enough to pay you a good amount of money for a job."

