// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL8-9_Task_08 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SecurityCaptain 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3393480314" "What're you doing here, {HeroName}? I have every right to arrest you on the spot!"
// Answer Text :
"P2994606397" "I just saved you! I think a 'thanks' is required."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3124769574" "...<br><br>Thanks for saving me. But I have more important things to do right now.<br><br><color orange>Overdrive groans and grips her side. You see she was hurt very badly by one of the Arachnoids. She's in no shape to fight through any more of them.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P50344631" "I've got this one covered."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1328306101" "You? What's the catch? Where's the stash of money you're looking for?"
// Answer Text :
"P1493069767" "This one's a freebie. Get out of here and let me handle this."
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P1899980660" "Alright... You'll need to disable two of the devices Arachnos is using to lure the Arachnoids here, followed by the main chemical container they have. All that will stop the Arachnoids from being lured into Paragon!"
// Answer Text :
"P1696819251" "Alright, I'll handle this."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1550561721" "Vernon Von Grun's (surprise surprise) mad plan is going to cause those Arachnoids to run loose through the streets of Paragon if something isn't done. There are plenty of heroes around that could stop that, but not before some serious damage is done. There's also a good chance Vernon Von Grun could get a promotion out of it, which is something that could cause even <i>more</i> problems down the line!"
// AcceptString :
"P3704678085" "Stop Vernon Von Grun's plan and save Overdrive"
// SendOffString :
"P1634641465" "You're able to find out the location of the sewers from what you overheard on the radio. You'll just have to hope you're not too late to save Overdrive and stop Vernon Von Grun."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P893142640" "Stop Vernon Von Grun's Arachnoid Invasion!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3172785742" "You need to get moving if you're going to stop Vernon Von Grun!"
// TaskTitle :
"P2596457904" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Maniacal Laughter</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3644084690" "You hear the unnerving sound of Arachnoid's scattering around the sewers."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2411430288" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Maniacal Laughter</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You exit the sewers to see a somewhat recovered Overdrive waiting for you. She extends her hand to you and nods.<br><br>'Thanks for the help, {HeroName}. Maybe I was wrong about you. Maybe you're not just out for yourself anymore. I hope, for your sake, you'll see how fulfilling this can be.'"

