// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P851429770" "I saw General Aarons on the news praising {HeroName}! Has he been brainwashed or something?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL8-9_Task_10 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - MrsPayday 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P1580162546" "You have my appreciation and my thanks. I assume you saw the video that was taken?<br><br>I have two other sisters that are being kept within this laboratory. Please, you have to help them! Crey plans on killing them once they learn of their secrets. We are all bound, our souls one. If one of them were to die, we would all die!"
// Answer Text :
"P212562113" "Alright, I'll save them. What about that reward?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3008875357" "Ah, yes. Here, now that I am free, I can create this for you.<br><br><color orange>The Cabal Witch spins her fingers as a small crystal appears in your hands.</color><br><br>This crystal will prevent you from getting headaches as long as you carry it. It was given to me by my mother on her deathbed, who was given it by her mother. It holds much personal value, but I will give it away to one as heroic as yourself. I must be off now, please, help the others!<br><br><color orange>... the reward was stopping you from getting <i>headaches</i>?</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1338150897" "... Headaches. Life saver. Thanks."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - BobbyPayday 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P1139796931" "Thank you so much, I'm eternally grateful for all of your help. Perhaps I was wrong about outsiders, you may not be so bad."
// Answer Text :
"P1891131702" "Right. So... that reward..."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P4048344108" "My sister promised you a reward? Hrm... Yes, you do deserve something for saving my life. Here. <br><br><color orange>The Witch twirls her fingers as a red orb appears in your hand.</color><br><br>This orb will be able to tell you the exact patterns of a weather forecast wherever you are. I do hope that is enough for you. This orb was passed down throughout my family for generations. It is one of the most valuable things that I have, but you deserve it now.<br><br>I must go join my sister, but please, there is still one of us left in there!<br><br><color orange>You're starting to get the feeling that these rewards <i>might</i> not really be what you bargained for.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P607726989" "Weather. Perfect."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SallyPayday 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3788828477" "Thank you so much! My sisters must have sent you, I'm sure.<br><br>I believe that no good deed should go unpunished. I do have a reward for you."
// Answer Text :
"P575076777" "Is it a family heirloom that you cherish and hold very dear to you?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2274264939" "<color orange>The witch looks at you with a raised eyebrow.</color><br><br>Yes, as a matter of fact, it is. This item was given to me by my mother, who received it from one of the great heroes of the Cabal. It has been treasured in my family for many years, but I am willing to part with it to give you thanks.<br><br><color orange>The witch twirls her fingers as a ring appears on the palm of your hand.</color><br><br>This ring will prevent the sun from burning your skin, though things such as fire and what not will still do the job. It was very useful for us when we would have to toil in the fields and work to earn the right to use our magic freely."
// Answer Text :
"P779791692" "Sun screen ring. You're the last one, right?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P2335233722" "I am, but Crey has documented what they've found on us so far. Please, you must destroy it or else they may use our own powers against us!<br><br>I will go to rejoin my sisters and we will spread the word of your brave deeds!"
// Answer Text :
"P2619403461" "... Alright."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - BlastFurnace 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3042359655" "What are you doing here, {HeroName}? Where are the witches? What have you done?"
// Answer Text :
"P3899361789" "I -rescued- them. RESCUED. For barely any reward, I'll have you know!"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1219281699" "... You did? But you did it for a reward! I can't believe -"
// Answer Text :
"P3332236563" "(Cut off Miss Thystle and explain what the rewards were)"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P694296824" "... Oh.<br><br>Well.<br><br>It looks like we really don't have any issues here. The day is won and the witches were saved. It was... er, good working with you, {HeroName}. I'll let the authorities know that there aren't any issues here."
// Answer Text :
"P1840212875" "Terrific."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1942656567" "You're not too sure where Crey's experiments are going to lead them, but it's just <i>too</i> bad for them that you're going to be rewarded by this witch and any other possible witches for saving their lives. You figure they could have some very powerful magical artifacts to give to you, especially if it means that they're going to be back with their sisters in Croatoa."
// AcceptString :
"P799420721" "Save the Cabal Witches!"
// SendOffString :
"P1419491704" "You'll have no time to lose. If Crey gets away with this experiment, they'll have new Paragon Protectors out in force <i>and</i> you'll never get that reward from those witches!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3040083883" "Save the Cabal from Crey"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1390161331" "Every minute wasted is time spent not getting that reward!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1335728935" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Gold Plated Monocle</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P931191106" "There's a magical air in the area. The Cabal are here and alive, along with their Crey captors. The Cabal are known for their powerful magics; it should be interesting to see what they would offer in exchange for their lives."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P422244053" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Gold Plated Monocle</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Well, you might as well have done this job for free. Out of all the powerful artifacts that the Cabal could've given you for their lives, you received items that will now allow you to not get headaches, never get sun burned, and you'll always be able to tell what the weather will be.<br><br>At least the authorities now have you listed under the, 'Do Not Arrest On Sight' page."

